            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Gairepertus"
                                >Ghairipert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">virum honestum</rs>
                        <foreign>vende a</foreign> viro venerabili <rs key="#Priests">presbites</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Tanualdus">Tanuald</name></persName> de
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/243">Sanctus
                            Richulo</orgName> da <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/673"
                            >Vuald[o]</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">particela</rs> mea et bone memorie <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="David">Davit</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Landed_possessions #Deacons"><name ref="Gallucius"
                                >Galluci</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">digachoni</rs> in loco qui dicitor at <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Munte at Panchule</placeName> prope <rs
                            key="#Gualdi #Fiscal_property #Mention #Emperor/king"><rs key="#Gualdi"
                                >Waldo</rs> domni <rs key="#Emperor/king">regi</rs></rs>; tamen
                        excepto parte de dui germani mei quondam Hildipert et Vitaliani, quemque
                        menime dededi; <foreign>dunque ora vende tre delle cinque parti
                            complessive</foreign>. Et da finis sunt: fine Sancti Richuli, et fine de
                        Tricchase, et fine de Aque Albule. <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: auris soledos
                        numero trinta. <foreign>Pena in duplum. Scrive:</foreign> Teutpert rationato
                        et amico meum. (…) Actum in Massa Robiani.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni:</foreign> + Gairepert viri honesti venditoris
                        (…) filio quondam Aruchis; + Hilprand <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"
                            >viri devoti</rs> nepotis eius; + Bandi <rs
                            key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs>
                        <rs key="#Other_minor_officer">centinarii</rs> testis; + Ermuli <rs
                            key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filius quondaam
                        Deusdonani de Versiciano testis; + Richipert <rs
                            key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filius quondam
                        Vitaliani testis. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: Teutpert scriptor.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>MDL IV/1, n. 45; reg. MDL V/2, n. 47; CDL I, n. 111, pp. 319-333; ChLA,
                    XXXII, 938.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                        <p/>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                        <p/>
                    </div>
                    <div type="commentary">
                         <p>Persone: Astolfo re; Ghairipert / Gairepert v. hon. (f. Aruchis; fr.
                    Vitaliani, Hildipert, Davit, Galluci; zio Hilprand); v. ven. pbr Tanuald de
                    Sanctus Richulo da Vualdo; Davit diac (fr. Vitaliani, Hildipert, Ghairipert,
                    Galluci); Galluci diac (fr. Vitaliani, Hildipert, Davit, Ghairipert); Hildipert
                    (fr. Vitaliani, Ghairipert, Davit, Galluci); Vitaliani (fr. Hildepert,
                    Ghairipert, Davit, Galluci); Robiani (?); Aruchis / Arochis (p. Ghairipert);
                    Hilprand v. dev. (nepos Ghairipert); Bandi v. dev. centinarii; Ermuli v. dev. de
                    Versiciano (f. Deusdonani); Deusdonani (p. Ermuli); Richipert v. dev. (f.
                    Vitaliani); Vitaliani (p. Richipert); Teutpert scriptor. Luoghi: Sanctus Richulo
                    da Vualdo [S. Regolo in Gualdo]; Munte at Panchule; Vualdo domni regi [Gualdo];
                    Tricchase [Tricasi]; Aque Albule; Massa Robiani; Versiciano [Verciano]. Chiese:
                    Sanctus Richulo da Vualdo [S. Regolo in Gualdo]. Cariche: Bandi v. dev.
                    centenarius. Note: Vualdo domni regi [Gualdo]; finis. Indice: s. regolo in
                    gualdo - compravendita - re - fines - maremma. Nota dorsale (sec XI-XII):
                    Cartula de terris in Pancule prope Gualdo. Niccolaj identifica lo scrittore con
                    l’autore di ChLA 927 = CDL 89 (un lucchese di Placule). Ne definisce la
                    scrittura «una minuscola piuttosto imperita e tarda, ignara di legature (…)
                    segnata di forme elementari». Munte =? Monte Balboli in Val di Cornia Tricasi </p>
                    </div>
